<p><strong>Medium humanoid (human, shapechanger), lawful good</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 12</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 31 (7d8)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft., fly 50 ft. in raven and hybrid forms</p>

